{"tid":1153452,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"美國女影星桃麗絲黛（Doris Day）與世長辭，享年97歲","createTime":"2019-05-13T15:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T08:31:48.000Z","uid":35221,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"19cd7e525a377adf195894e13762dbdbf858b30a","tid":1153452,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"美國女影星桃麗絲黛與世長辭享年97歲<br />\n2019年05月13日 09:52<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.singtao.ca/wp-content/uploads/master_sandbox/2019/05/2019051322003213908.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.singtao.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster_sandbox%2F2019%2F05%2F2019051322003213908.jpg&h=7d81f05e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國著名女歌手和女電影演員桃麗絲黛（Doris Day）於13日在位於加州的家中與世長辭，享年97歲。發言人證實，她是感染肺炎逝世，親友都在身邊陪著。<br />\n<br />\n桃麗絲黛是1950年代至1960年代美國最受歡迎的女歌手之一，更有電影「票房皇后」之稱，是當時最受歡迎的女演員。桃麗絲黛曾在2008年獲得葛萊美頒發的終身成就獎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://invisibleworkfilmwritings.files.wordpress.com/2014/07/pillowtalkposter.jpg?w=702\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finvisibleworkfilmwritings.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F07%2Fpillowtalkposter.jpg%3Fw%3D702&h=db74bbe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://playitagain.info/site/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/Pillow-Talk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplayitagain.info%2Fsite%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F01%2FPillow-Talk.gif&h=8e3cfa37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n桃麗絲黛祖父母來自德國，她本人在美國出生長大，代表作《碧海笙歌》（Romance on the High Seas）、《西點軍校的故事》(The West Point Story)等。尤其電影《碧海笙歌》中其陽光形像很快就獲得觀眾喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n桃麗絲黛在50年代終於成為一顆影歌雙棲的紅星。她不但歌曲唱的好，還有最廣為人知的經典金曲，1956年希治閣驚悚經典「擒兇記」(The Man Who Knew Too Much) 電影主題曲《Que Sera Sera》，得到奧斯卡金像獎最佳原創歌曲獎，後來也登上英國歌壇榜首。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xZbKHDPPrrc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxZbKHDPPrrc&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=04fe0f53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xZbKHDPPrrc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://playitagain.info/site/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/Man-Who-Knew-Too-Much1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplayitagain.info%2Fsite%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F01%2FMan-Who-Knew-Too-Much1.jpg&h=4cabe7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/chiamin0513/1391736347-290793038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fchiamin0513%2F1391736347-290793038.jpg&h=d5aba097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Que Sera Sera》連同《Sentimental Journey》、1953年西部片「災禍珍妮」獲獎主題曲《Secret Love》一起被收錄到葛萊美名人堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/3448388/2019-05-13/news-美國女影星桃麗絲黛與世長辭享年97歲/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F3448388%2F2019-05-13%2Fnews-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E5%BD%B1%E6%98%9F%E6%A1%83%E9%BA%97%E7%B5%B2%E9%BB%9B%E8%88%87%E4%B8%96%E9%95%B7%E8%BE%AD%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B497%E6%AD%B2%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=d265d922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/3448388/2019-05-13/news-美國女影星桃麗絲黛與世長辭享年97歲/?variant=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"da2651b3535f20d21ed364f9115c556713f759f7","tid":1153452,"uid":143093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"Just tea for two and two for tea<br />\nJust me for you and you for me alone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5336be35bd8d0d45f9adb99c8c52d2970584ff07","tid":1153452,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"da2651b3535f20d21ed364f9115c556713f759f7","tid":1153452,"uid":143093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:48:37.000Z"