w.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfU8tQpCZEzg&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=ca4c6b11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fU8tQpCZEzg</a><br />\n<br />\nFly Me To The Moon (1965)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j7bfudsfZjw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dj7bfudsfZjw&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=c4264761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j7bfudsfZjw</a>"},{"pid":"ea96f97650679d7d5fd7cfb5a0c5a46c80a0efda","tid":1153452,"uid":97340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:54:46.000Z","msg":"喂&hellip;&hellip; 俾個明星名你估<br />\n四個字既<br />\nMichael Jackson<br />\n唔係唔係 最尾個字係器官<br />\n菲丹娜蕙<br />\n唔係 低啲<br />\n桃麗絲黛<br />\n唔係 <br />\n咁係乜啊<br />\n係泰迪羅賓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個第一次聽佢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6897af1b2c48981842789cdb9d457598ae6d0727","tid":1153452,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea96f97650679d7d5fd7cfb5a0c5a46c80a0efda","tid":1153452,"uid":97340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:54:46.000Z","msg":"喂&hellip;&hellip; 俾個明星名你估<br />\n四個字既<br />\nMichael Jackson<br />\n唔係唔係 最尾個字係器官<br />\n菲丹娜蕙<br />\n唔係 低啲<br />\n桃麗絲黛<br />\n唔係 <br />\n咁係乜啊<br />\n係泰迪羅賓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細個第一次聽佢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 皮球大合唱"}]}